{
  "stem": "17299.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 292.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was 90% water and a potato and a carrot in it, but it was warm, and it was bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then a Russian-- he must have been an officer, the interpreter-- turns his face to the wall while we were eating the soup, and said, I'm talking to the wall that the Germans can't see that I talk to you, because I will be beaten up otherwise.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In a few months you will be looking just like we do, and you will be dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Germans will not feed you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They will abuse you, and you are expendable just like we are.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't believe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- we looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were a week in the ghetto, and-- we are six days in the ghetto, and we had not get-- gotten a slice of bread yet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We told them what the Russian had said, and they-- and they were shocked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said, I-- I-- I don't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans are not animals like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very few.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had a little surprise there on the fourth or fifth night in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some Latvian SS broke in the house and raped one of the girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I will not mention the name, because she's still alive and is in-- lives in New York.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the Latvian police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three came in the house, held everyone at bay with a rifle, and then they rape the girl.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everyone said now we know we are in for trouble-- quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the last day we were-- and I think on December 21, everyone got a slice of bread, 100 grams of bread, which is equivalent to three ounces.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
